title: Some early Nexus 6P orders now shipping from the Google Store
text:
Some early Nexus 6P orders now shipping from the Google Store 
Published By: AndroidCentral.com - Today 
Following a bit of a wait, it looks like those who got in early on Nexus 6P pre-orders from the Google Store are starting to see their order...
